%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Intuit's%20Humera%20Shahid%20on%202024%3A%20I%20want%20to%20make%20work%20a%20safe%20place%20for%20employees%20going%20through%20challenging%20times%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22910%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Humera%20Shahid.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657c860b7a3c8094d5dd8ac5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22682%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIntuit's%20Humera%20Shahid.%3Cp%3EIntuit%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EHumera%20Shahid%20works%20on%20diversity%2C%20equity%2C%20and%20inclusion%20and%20talent%20development%20at%20Intuit.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShahid%20says%20she%20wants%20to%20support%20employees%20so%20work%20can%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bsafe%20space.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShahid's%20insights%20are%20part%20of%20Business%20Insider's%20year-end%20leadership%20series%2C%20%26quot%3BLooking%20Ahead%202024.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EHumera%20Shahid%20is%20Intuit's%20chief%20diversity%2C%20equity%2C%20and%20inclusion%20officer%20and%20vice%20president%20of%20talent%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20quite%20a%20title%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20said%20to%20her%20recently.%20%26quot%3BHow%20does%20that%20work%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20most%20important%20parts%20of%20creating%20a%20diverse%2C%20equitable%2C%20and%20inclusive%20workplace%20is%20the%20role%20your%20manager%20plays%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BManagers%20make%20a%20lot%20of%20decisions%20around%20'Who%20am%20I%20going%20to%20hire%3F'%20When%20you%20combine%20the%20power%20of%20'How%20does%20the%20manager%20create%20the%20right%20environment%3F'%20and%20do%20all%20of%20these%20things%20to%20really%20advance%20our%20DEI%20strategy%20for%20employees%2C%20it%20felt%20like%20it%20made%20sense%20at%20the%20time%20to%20combine%20these%20two%20things%20together.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShahid%20has%20been%20at%20Intuit%2C%20which%20owns%20software%20products%20including%C2%A0the%20email-marketing%20service%20Mailchimp%2C%20the%20tax-filing%20software%20TurboTax%2C%20and%20the%20credit-rating%20service%20Credit%20Karma%2C%20since%202019.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20hired%20to%20do%20talent-development%20work%20and%20to%20kind%20of%20rebuild%20that%20function%20for%20the%20organization%20as%20we%20were%20going%20through%20a%20massive%20business%20transformation%20to%20become%20an%20AI-driven%20platform%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShahid%20said%20she%20asks%20herself%20about%20the%20shift's%20implications%20for%20talent.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20kind%20of%20talent%20do%20we%20need%20in%20terms%20of%20leadership%20and%20management%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BHow%20do%20we%20develop%20that%20talent%3F%20How%20do%20we%20then%20build%20the%20skills%20for%20all%20the%20learning%20and%20development%20for%20what%20we%20need%20in%20the%20future%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20she's%20proud%20of%20how%20Intuit%20helps%20managers%20talk%20to%20and%20support%20their%20direct%20reports%20during%20challenging%20personal%20and%20political%20times%2C%20partially%20through%20providing%20trainings%20and%20guides%20for%20managers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%202%20%C2%BD%20years%20into%20her%20career%20at%20Intuit%2C%20she%20was%20also%20asked%20to%20take%20on%20DEI.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20I%20love%20about%20it%20is%20the%20willingness%20to%20learn%20about%20different%20people's%20experiences%20and%20how%20that%20shows%20up%20in%20the%20workplace%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShahid's%20insights%20are%20part%20of%20Business%20Insider's%20year-end%20leadership%20series%2C%20%26quot%3BLooking%20Ahead%202024%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20digs%20into%20vision%2C%20strategy%2C%20and%20challenges%20across%20corporate%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20following%20conversation%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20one%20thing%20you're%20excited%20about%20for%202024%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20able%20to%20have%20technology%20work%20side%20by%20side%20with%20people%20%E2%80%94%20how%20it%20will%20make%20them%20better%2C%20do%20their%20work%20faster%2C%20be%20able%20to%20learn%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20builds%20this%20agility%20and%20speed%20automatically.%20So%20I'm%20just%20excited%20to%20explore%20that%20with%20our%20employees%20%E2%80%94%20and%20feel%20like%20we%20can%20do%20more%20than%20we%20thought%20possible%20by%20taking%20advantage%20of%20technology%2C%20and%20not%20being%20afraid%20but%20just%20leaning%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20really%20excited%20about%20what%20the%20future%20will%20bring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20you%20most%20concerned%20about%20for%202024%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20lot%20going%20on%20in%20the%20world%20today%2C%20and%20I%20think%20COVID%20taught%20us%3A%20How%20do%20you%20really%20help%20manage%20the%20well-being%20and%20even%20energy%20levels%20of%20our%20employees%20as%20you%20think%20about%20things%20that%20are%20going%20on%20that%20are%20affecting%20them%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20day%20those%20things%20become%20bigger%20and%20bigger.%20There's%20so%20much%20coming%20at%20people%2C%20whether%20it's%20an%20election%20year%20that%20impacts%20you%20or%20whether%20you're%20dealing%20with%20something%20with%20a%20family%20member.%20There%20are%20just%20so%20many%20things%20that%20happen%20in%20life%20that%20affect%20you%20at%20work%2C%20and%20so%20I%20worry%20about%20our%20ability%20to%20keep%20supporting%20our%20employees%20in%20every%20way%20possible%20%E2%80%94%20and%20providing%20a%20safe%2C%20inclusive%20place%20to%20do%20that%20while%20also%20doing%20great%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20worry%20about%20our%20mental%20well-being%20across%20the%20board%2C%20for%20all%20of%20us.%20Work%20and%20community%20can%20actually%20be%20a%20really%20safe%20space%20where%20you%20can%20be%20yourself%20and%20you%20can%20share.%20I%20don't%20want%20people%20suffering%20in%20silence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20one%20thing%20you%20think%20you%20got%20right%20in%202023%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20as%20a%20company%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20on%20manager%20accountability%20and%20DEI%20together.%20As%20large%20social%20issues%20impact%20our%20employees%2C%20how%20do%20we%20prepare%20managers%20to%20check%20in%20with%20our%20employees%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20they%20can%20provide%20the%20right%20support%20and%20resources%3F%20And%20just%20to%20acknowledge%20them%20as%20people%20when%20something%20tough%20is%20happening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20created%20the%20guides%2C%20we%20started%20to%20think%20about%20what%20the%20use%20cases%20would%20be.%20I%20think%20we%20were%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20this%20is%20really%20going%20to%20be%20important%20as%20we%20talk%20about%20issues%20around%20race.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20there's%20an%20act%20of%20violence%20affecting%20a%20specific%20community%2C%20this%20is%20a%20really%20helpful%20way%20to%20acknowledge%20it%2C%20to%20own%20it%2C%20to%20create%20space%20for%20people.%20There%20are%20prompts%20for%20how%20you%20can%20have%20the%20conversation%2C%20what%20you%20can%20say%2C%20if%20you%20need%20help%2C%20how%20to%20contact%20HR.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20didn't%20imagine%20that%20as%202023%20went%20on%20we%20would%20want%20to%20use%20those%20same%20guides%20for%20people%20struggling%20with%20reproductive%20rights.%20We%20will%20use%20those%20same%20guides%20when%20thinking%20about%20different%20legislation%20introduced%20around%20LGBTQ%2B%20rights.%20We%20use%20those%20same%20guides%20as%20we%20saw%20what%20happened%20with%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20and%20that%20conflict%20and%20employees%20wanting%20to%20talk%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20intention%20was%20to%20have%20something%20that%20was%20durable.%20We%20prepared%20our%20managers%20on%20how%20to%20lead%20with%20empathy%20and%20curiosity%20and%20compassion%20and%20gave%20them%20resources%20to%20do%20that.%20Fortunately%20or%20unfortunately%2C%20we've%20been%20able%20to%20use%20them%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20situations%20that%20are%20really%20personal%20and%20meaningful%20to%20different%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20one%20thing%20you%20got%20wrong%20in%202023%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWrong%20is%20such%20a%20strong%20word%2C%20because%20I'm%20such%20a%20learner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20things%20I%20wish%20we%20would%20have%20done%20more%20of%2C%20or%20differently%3A%20We%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20wanting%20to%20grow%20our%20employees'%20skills%2C%20and%20I%20think%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20areas%20where%20we%20could%20continue%20to%20actually%20build%20more%20skills%20and%20upskill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20just%20starting%20on%20our%20AI%20learning%20journey.%20Could%20we%20have%20done%20that%20three%20months%20earlier%3F%20It's%20just%20about%20operating%20with%20speed%20and%20being%20able%20to%20do%20that%20quickly%2C%20at%20the%20right%20time%2C%20in%20a%20concerted%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20it's%20probably%20just%20doing%20things%20a%20little%20bit%20faster%20than%20we%20would%20have%20imagined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fintuit-dei-talent-humera-shahid-managers-ai-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703416681000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657c86480ec98e92f74fff17%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fintuit-dei-talent-humera-shahid-managers-ai-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Intuit's%20Humera%20Shahid%20helps%20managers%20support%20their%20employees'%20well-being%20with%20empathy%2C%20curiosity%2C%20and%20compassion.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jrose%40insider.com%20(Jos%C3%A9e%20Rose)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%