0battle.%20So%20we%20are%20running%20almost%20from%20a%20caste%20perspective%20an%20apartheid%20system.%20So%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20I%20am%20trying%20to%20change.%20Because%20the%20entire%20system%20is%20controlled%20by%20a%20very%20thin%20group%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%2C%20along%20with%20members%20of%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20has%20been%20demanding%20a%20nationwide%20caste%20census.%20In%20the%20recently%20concluded%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Telangana%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%20promised%20a%20caste%20census%20in%20its%20manifestos.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20party%20however%2C%20only%20won%20in%20Telangana%20and%20was%20voted%20out%20of%20power%20in%20the%20three%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-has-no-option-but-to-recover-in-heartland-states-in-2024%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EHindi%20heartland%20states%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20also%20promised%20to%20conduct%20such%20a%20survey%20if%20it%20is%20voted%20to%20power%20in%20the%20general%20election%20in%202024.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fwhy-the-bjp-is-afraid-of-a-caste-census%5C%22%3EWhy%20the%20BJP%20Is%20Afraid%20of%20a%20Caste%20Census%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20has%20earlier%20pressed%20for%20the%20need%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20saying%20that%20it%20reveals%20the%20composition%20of%20OBC%2C%20Dalit%20and%20Adivasi%20communities%20in%20the%20country%20which%20will%20will%20open%20up%20a%20window%20for%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fcongress-state-governments-caste-and-socio-economic-surveys-cwc%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cnew%20development%20paradigm%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%