20ensuring%20that%20women%20had%20completed%20all%20their%20weaving%20before%20the%20holiday%2C%20that%20their%20homes%20were%20tidy%2C%20that%20children%20weren't%20naughty%2C%20and%20that%20people%20were%20participating%20in%20celebratory%20feasts%2C%20Smith%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20unlike%20Santa's%20comparatively%20benign%20habit%20of%20giving%20out%20coal%2C%20Perchta's%20punishment%20was%20to%20slit%20open%20the%20sinner's%20stomach%2C%20remove%20their%20organs%2C%20and%20stuff%20them%20with%20rocks%20and%20straw%20before%20sewing%20them%20back%20up%2C%20according%20to%20Smith's%20essay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20even%20those%20who%20didn't%20eat%20a%20traditional%20meal%20of%20fish%20and%20gruel%20on%20her%20feast%20day%20would%20get%20their%20bellies%20slit%2C%20according%20to%20Morris.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Perchta%20wasn't%20all%20bad%20%E2%80%94%20for%20those%20who%20behaved%2C%20she'd%20leave%20a%20small%20silver%20coin%20in%20their%20shoe%2C%20according%20to%20Morris.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20legend%20of%20Perchta%20dates%20back%20centuries%2C%20she%20is%20still%20celebrated%20in%20parts%20of%20Germany%20and%20Austria%20today%2C%20like%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.salzburg.info%2Fen%2Fsalzburg%2Fadvent%2Fkrampus-percht%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESalzburg's%20annual%20Krampus%20and%20Perchten%20Parades%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20masked%20marauders%20storm%20the%20streets%20to%20scare%20off%20the%20evil%20spirits%20of%20winter%2C%20like%20Perchta.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faustria-bavaria-christmas-villain-demon-frau-perchta-witch-disembowels-victims-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703415121000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657b6e3250edbc52a86471ab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faustria-bavaria-christmas-villain-demon-