of%20genocide%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20in%20Gaza%2C%20but%20wherever%20else%20there%20is%20oppression%20and%20cruelty%2C%20the%20church%20must%20practice%20the%20true%20meaning%20of%20Christmas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20true%20meaning%20of%20Christmas%20is%20found%20in%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FThe_American_Magazine%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20American%20Magazine%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(1889).%20I%20quote%3A%20Christmas%20calls%20on%20Christians%20%E2%80%9Cto%20give%20up%20one%E2%80%99s%20very%20self%20%E2%80%93%20to%20think%20only%20of%20others%20%E2%80%93%20how%20to%20bring%20the%20greatest%20happiness%20to%20others.%E2%80%9D%20That%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20demands%20sacrifice.%20For%20Christ%E2%80%99s%20journey%20itself%20was%20a%20journey%20from%20%E2%80%98The%20manger%20to%20the%20Cross%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20a%20thorny%20path%20in%20which%20he%20confronted%20the%20rich%2C%20powerful%2C%20and%20cruel.%20To%20claim%20Christmas%20as%20a%20festival%20of%20peace%2C%20love%2C%20and%20hope%2C%20is%20to%20engage%20in%20costly%20solidarity%20with%20the%20weak%20and%20powerless.%20Or%20else%2C%20we%20will%20be%20emptying%20Christmas%20from%20its%20very%20essence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMay%20this%20Christmas%20season%20be%20a%20time%20when%20humankind%2C%20as%20a%20whole%2C%20can%20aspire%20to%20a%20just%20world%20where%20death%20and%20destruction%20are%20left%20behind%20and%20an%20authentic%20peace%20be%20positioned%20through%20constant%20dialogue.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3ERanjan%20Solomon%20is%20a%20political%20commentator%2Fhuman%20rights%20activist%2C%20and%20a%20long-time%20Palestine%20solidarity%20advocate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703414769000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F24161457%2FScreenshot-2023-12-24-at-4.09.24.png%22%2C%2