%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erobot%20can%20crank%20out%2080%20bowls%20an%20hour%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20cutting%20labor%20by%2050%25%2C%20Business%20Insider's%20Meghan%20Morris%20reported%20in%20mid-December.%20Lab37%2C%20which%20is%20a%20Pittsburgh-based%20unit%20of%20CloudKitchen's%20parent%20company%2C%20is%20developing%20the%20robot.%20Eric%20Meyhofer%2C%20formerly%20the%20head%20of%20Uber's%20self-driving%20unit%2C%20runs%20Lab37.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECanada%20food%20hall%20debuts%20automated%20salad%20and%20bowl%20making%20machine.%20Next%20up%2C%20the%20US.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cibotica's%20automated%20salad%20and%20bowl%20making%20machine%20Remy%20launched%20in%20early%20December.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657a09740ec98e92f74f1f92%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221334%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECibotica's%20automated%20salad%20and%20bowl%20making%20machine%20Remy%20launched%20in%20early%20December.%3Cp%3ECibotica%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRatatouille%26quot%3B%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20big%20inspiration%20for%20these%20culinary-focused%20robotics%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECibotica%20is%20a%20Vancouver%2C%20Canada-based%20company%20that%20recently%20debuted%20an%20automated%20salad%20and%20bowl%20making%20machine.%20It's%20called%20Remy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECibotica's%20Remy%20launched%20in%20early%20December%20at%20a%20digital-focused%20food%20hall%20in%20Canada%20called%20Food%20Republic.%20The%20machine%20makes%20up%20to%20300%20salads%20per%20hour.%20Next%20year%2C%20a%20Seattle-based%20pizza%20chain%20named%20Moto%20plans%20to%20use%20Remy%20to%20expand%20its%20menu%20by%20offering%20salads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECibotica%20said%20its%20automated%20under-the-counter%20makeline%20can%20help%20restaurants%20save%20up%20to%2030%25%20on%20labor%20costs.%20Co-founder%20and%20co-CEO%20Ashkan%20Mirnabavi%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20a%20recent%2