n-bag-realreal-handbag-expert-so-expensive-2019-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHerm%C3%A8s%20Birkin%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20perhaps%20the%20most%20exclusive%20and%20expensive%20type%20of%20handbag%20in%20the%20world.%20With%20a%20starting%20price%20of%20%249%2C000%2C%20it's%20not%20surprising%20it's%20a%20popular%20gift%20for%20those%20who%20also%20have%20exclusive%20and%20expensive%20taste.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Chesterfield's%20contacts%20gives%20a%20new%20Herm%C3%A8s%20bag%20to%20his%20wife%20each%20year%2C%20and%20the%20color%20of%20the%20purse%20sets%20the%20tone%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20her%20gifts.%20A%20red%20bag%2C%20for%20example%2C%20will%20be%20surrounded%20by%20red%20items%20from%20other%20luxury%20retailers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Pollard%20Bayme's%20clients%20requested%20a%20rare%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-the-iconic-hermes-birkin-handbag-was-invented-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHimalayan%20Birkin%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20diamond%20hardware%20for%20a%20particularly%20special%20gift.%20Crafted%20from%20dyed%20crocodile%20skin%2C%20the%20bag%20cost%20%24750%2C000%20and%20required%20security%20to%20deliver%20it%20to%20the%20client.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20person%20that%20has%20everything%2C%20why%20not%20have%20diamonds%20on%20your%20handbag%20too%3F%26quot%3B%20Pollard%20Bayme%20said.%20Why%20not%2C%20indeed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20trip%20to%20space%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ultimate%20flex%20for%20the%20billionaire%20class%26quot%3B%20is%20two%20tickets%20to%20space%2C%20Pollard%20Bayme%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20in%20the%20footsteps%20of%20billionaires%20like%20Jeff%20Bezos%20and%20Richard%20Branson%2C%20two%20of%20her%20clients%20are%20heading%20into%20orbit%20for%20the%20holiday.%20The%20gift%20also%20includes%20training%20with%20NASA%20astronauts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Pollard%20Bayme%20did%20not%20disclose%20how%20much%20her%20clients%20were%20paying%20for%20the%20unusual%20vacation%2C%20a%20seat%20on%20Branson's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvirgin-galactic-blue-origin-spacex-commercial-space-flights-tourism-cost-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EVirgin%20Galactic%20flight%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20go%20for%20%24450%2C000%20each%2C%20while%20one%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeff-bezos-blue-origin-spaceflight-ken-griffin-8-million-teacher-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EBezos'%20Blue%20Origin%20rockets%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20cost%20millions.%20At%20that%20price%2C%20BI%20hopes%20the%20champagne%20up%20there%20is%20very%20well-chilled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20wellness%20retreat%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20very%20best%20gear%20to%20go%20with%20it%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThough%20the%20other%20gifts%20on%20this%20list%20prove%20that%20excessive%20opulence%20isn't%20dead%2C%20Chesterfield%20said%20many%20of%20his%20contacts%20are%20choosing%20to%20give%20experiences%2C%20and%20forgoing%20presents%20like%20jewelry%20and%20cars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20seem%20to%20be%20a%20bit%20exhausted%20with%20what%20you'd%20call%20hard%20luxury%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Instead%2C%20they're%20giving%20travel%20experiences%2C%20particularly%20wellness%20retreats%20like%20a%20bike%20trip%20through%20Mallorca%20or%20a%20week%20at%20Austria's%20Vivamayr%20spa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20even%20though%20these%20gifts%20are%20not%20emblazoned%20with%20designer%20names%20or%20encrusted%20with%20gems%2C%20they're%20not%20cheap.%20The%20bike%20tour%20starts%20at%20%245%2C999%2C%20for%20example%2C%20while%20a%20stay%20at%20Vivamayr%20costs%20a%20minimum%20of%20%242%2C500.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20to%20really%20round%20out%20the%20gift%2C%20a%20stocking%20stuffer%20of%20the%20best%20of%20the%20best%20gear%20can't%20hurt%2C%20like%20a%20%243%2C450%20Loro%20Piana%20windbreaker%20or%20%242%2C000%20Monc