ion%20at%20the%20site%20of%20Itaewon%20disaster%2C%20Yongsan%20district%20on%20October%2031%2C%202022%20in%20Seoul%2C%20South%20Korea.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6586f4dfab6f2ebb11f6a256%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESouth%20Korea's%20National%20Policy%20Agency%20has%20been%20targeting%20organized%20crime%20rings.%20%3Cp%3ENurPhoto%20%2F%20Getty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESouth%20Korea's%20National%20Police%20Agency%20has%20been%20targeting%20organized%20crime%20rings%20across%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20majority%20of%20those%20arrested%20lately%20are%20Gen%20Z%20or%20millennials%20below%20the%20age%20of%2030.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20younger%20criminals%20have%20also%20shifted%20away%20from%20violence%20towards%20fraud%20and%20gambling%20crimes%2C%20The%20Korea%20Herald%20reported.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESouth%20Korean%20police%20have%20been%20cracking%20down%20on%20organized%20crime%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20and%20authorities%20have%20announced%20that%20a%20majority%20of%20those%20they%20have%20been%20arresting%20are%20Gen%20Z%20or%20millennials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20country's%20National%20Police%20Agency%20(NPA)%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20that%201%2C183%20members%20of%20organized%20crime%20rings%20had%20been%20arrested%20across%20the%20country%20between%20August%207%20and%20December%2016%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.koreaherald.com%2Fview.php%3Fud%3D20231220000548%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Korea%20Herald%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20888%20of%20those%20arrested%20were%20%26quot%3BMZ%20gangsters%26quot%3B%20who%20were%20younger%20than%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELaw%20enforcement%20sources%20said%20that%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20crimes%20being%20committed%20by%20the%20younger%20criminals%20had%20changed%20compared%20to%20that%20of%20older%20generations%2C%20with%20more%20instances%20of%20online%20gambling%2C%20scams%2C%20and%20fraud%20being%20seen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolice%20said%20that%20nearly%2040%25%20of%20the%20charges%20involved%20%26quot%3Bintricate%2Fbusiness-type%20illegal%20activities%2C%26quot%3B%20such%20as%20running%20online%20gambling%20sites%2C%20while%20just%20over%2021%25%20were%20for%20extortion%20and%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20workshop%20designed%20to%20help%20prosecutors%20working%20on%20these%20cases%2C%20attendees%20were%20told%20that%20the%20MZ%20gangsters%20%26quot%3Bjoin%20forces%20based%20on%20profit%2C%20rather%20than%20based%20on%20factions%20like%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetimes.co.uk%2Farticle%2Fhundreds-of-next-generation-south-korean-gangsters-arrested-xxrxf7nqd%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20need%20for%20authorities%20to%20re-establish%20the%20meaning%20of%20organised%20crime%20rings%2C%20and%20find%20ways%20to%20respond%20to%20such%20crimes%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20workshop%20was%20told.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20NPA%20spokesperson%20told%20The%20Times%20that%20the%20agency%20would%20%26quot%3Bstrengthen%20the%20gang%20crackdown%20system%20to%20establish%20a%20more%20effective%20crime%20response%20system%20and%20focus%20our%20investigative%20capabilities%20on%20various%20forms%20of%20organised%20crime%20centred%20on%20MZ%20generation%20gangsters.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Focindex.net%2Fcountry%2Fkorea_rep%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOrganized%20Crime%20Index%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20provides%20metrics%20on%20organized%20crime%20around%20the%20world%2C%20South%20Korean%20authorities%20have%20been%20pushing%20to%20rid%20the%20country%20of%20%26quot%3Ball%20mafia-style%20groups%26quot%3B%20since%20the%201990s%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20few%20remaining%20organizations%20are%20small%20and%20do%20not