ed%20since%20violence%20began%20on%20May%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shutdown%20called%20by%20the%20Kuki%20groups%2C%20however%2C%20puts%20the%20first%20small%20steps%20to%20peace%20at%20risk.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20posted%20extra%20security%20forces%20on%20the%20two%20highways%20to%20resume%20bus%20services%20from%20the%20state%20capital%20Imphal%20to%20Mao%20to%20the%20north%2C%20passing%20via%20Kangpokpi%2C%20and%20from%20Imphal%20to%20Churachandpur%20to%20the%20south.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20two%20routes%20pass%20through%20hill%20and%20valley%20areas%20that%20have%20seen%20violence%20between%20the%20hill-majority%20Kuki%20tribes%20and%20the%20valley-majority%20Meiteis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20buses%20that%20left%20for%20Mao%2C%20110%20km%20from%20Imphal%2C%20returned%20midway%20after%20facing%20a%20large%20number%20of%20protesters%20who%20blocked%20the%20road%20in%20Kangpokpi%2C%20despite%20the%20presence%20of%20security%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVisuals%20show%20people%20armed%20with%20single-barrel%20guns%20among%20the%20crowds%20stopping%20vehicles%20before%20allowing%20them%20to%20proceed%20after%20checking%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fbjpffbi8_manipur-blockade_625x300_24_December_23.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20buses%20that%20went%20to%20Churachandpur%2C%2065%20km%20from%20the%20state%20capital%2C%20could%20not%20enter%20the%20hill%20district%20as%20the%20Kuki%20tribes%20have%20blocked%20access%20following%20directions%20from%20the%20Kuki%20group%20Indigenous%20Tribal%20Leaders'%20Forum%20(ITLF)%2C%20which%20said%20they%20have%20intelligence%20inputs%20about%20possible%20attempt%20to%20disrupt%20the%20Christmas%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stand-off%20in%20Kangpokpi%20led%20to%20tensions%20after%20the%20crowds%20came%20in%20front%20of%20the%20buses%20escorted%20by%20the%20security%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20this%2C%20the%20Governor's%20scheduled%20programme%20to%20inaugurate%20pre-fabricated%20homes%20at%20Kangpokpi's%20subdivision%20Champhai.%20The%20protesters%20also%20forced%20shops%20and%20businesses%20to%20pull%20down%20shutters.%20Though%20they%20did%20not%20stop%20the%20vehicles%20from%20passing%20the%20area%2C%20they%20stopped%20the%20buses%20and%20frisked%20the%20passengers%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur%20has%20already%20seen%20a%20%26quot%3Bdark%20Diwali%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20gloomiest%20Ningol%20Chakouba%2C%20which%20the%20Meitei%20community%20celebrates%20after%20Diwali%2C%20and%20is%20similar%20to%20Bhai%20Dooj%20except%20that%20in%20Manipur%20it%20is%20the%20brothers%20who%20welcome%20their%20sisters%20from%20their%20matrimonial%20homes%20for%20a%20grand%20feast.%20Christmas%2C%20too%2C%20is%20a%20gloomy%20time%20in%20Manipur%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Kangpokpi-based%20Kuki%20group%20has%20asked%20the%20state%20government%20to%20withdraw%20the%20order%20for%20posting%20more%20security%20forces%20along%20the%20National%20Highway%20to%20prevent%20any%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Churachandpur%2C%20the%20ITLF%20has%20said%20all%20non-tribals%20within%20the%20district%20are%20not%20allowed%20to%20move%20out%20and%20non-tribal%20from%20outside%20are%20can't%20move%20inside%20the%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuestions%20have%20been%20raised%20over%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20civil%20society%20groups%20whose%20aggressive%20actions%20appear%20to%20be%20only%20fuelling%20tensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20told%20NDTV%20on%20Saturday%20it%20was%20expected%20that%20in%20the%20initial%20days%2C%20many%20people%20would%20not%20turn%20up%2C%20especially%20after%20Kuki%20civil%20society%20groups%20opposed%20the%20move%20to%20open%20the%20highways.%20What%20is%20inexplicable%20is%20the%20shutdown%20of%20the%20districts%20by%20pressure%20groups%20when%20the%20authorities%20have%20ensured%20safe%20commute%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20adding%20they%20have%20come%20across%20hundreds%20of%20people%20who%20fled%20their%20burning%20homes%20and%20want%20to%20return%20to%20rebuild%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kuki%20groups'%20move%20to%20shut%20down%20the%20districts%20stem%20from%20their%20allegations%20that%20the%20Manipur%20Police%20functioned%20with%20bias%20in%20how%20they%20operated%20amid%20the%20violence.%20The%20Manipur%20government's%20attempt%20to%20send%20police%20personnel%20in%20the%20hill%20districts%20where%20the%20Kuki%20tribes%20are%20settled%20had%20also%20faced%20strong%20resistance%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20border%20town%20Moreh%20near%20Myanmar%2C%20Churachandpur%2C%20and%20Kangpokpi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20November%2029%20specifically%20pointed%20out%20the%20role%20of%20some%20civil%20society%20groups%20in%20keeping%20tensions%20in%20Manipur%20simmering%2C%20during%20a%20hearing%20on%20burying%20bodies%20kept%20in%20morgues.%20Ordering%20the%20petitioners%20to%20bury%20the%20dead%20respectfully%20in%20designated%20sites%20instead%20of%20government%20land%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20said%20the%20petition%20appeared%20like%20an%20%26quot%3Bidea%20only%20to%20keep%20the%20pot%20boiling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20extra%20security%20forces%20deployed%20for%20highway%20security%20are%20led%20by%20Indian%20Police%20Service%20(IPS)%20officers%20Nishit%20Kumar%20Ujjwal%20and%20K%20Kabib.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703409600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fidms5hkg_manipur-blockade_625x300_24_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fblockades-test-manipurs-move-to-open-highways-bring-normalcy-4733484%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Manipur%20government's%20decision%20to%20open%20two%20key%20highways%20in%20the%20state%20is%20facing%20resistance%20in%20the%20hill%20areas.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fblockades-test-manipurs-move-to-open-highways-bring-normalcy-4733484%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fblockades-test-manipurs-move-to-open-highways-bring-normalcy-4733484%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fblockades-test-manipurs-move-to-open-highways-bring-normalcy-4733484%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tejashwi%20Yadav's%20Response%20To%20DMK%20MP's%20%26quot%3BBihar%20People%20Clean%20Toilets%26quot%3B%20Video%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20video%20of%20DMK%20leader%20Dayanidhi%20Maran%2C%20which%20party%20sources%20claim%20is%20old%2C%20can%20spell%20trouble%20for%20the%20unity%20of%20INDIA%20bloc%20at%20a%20time%20when%20it%20is%20gearing%20up%20for%20the%20big%20Lok%20Sabha%20contest%20just%20a%20few%20months%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%2C%20the%20authenticity%20of%20which%20NDTV%20cannot%20verify%2C%20DMK%20MP%20Dayanidhi%20Maran%20is%20heard%20comparing%20the%20job%20prospects%20of%20those%20who%20have%20studied%20only%20Hindi%20with%20those%20who%20know%20English.%20In%20this%20context%2C%20he%20says%20those%20who%20study%20only%20Hindi%20in%20Bihar%20%26quot%3Bbuild%20houses%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bclean%20toilets%26quot%3B%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnly%20because%20they%20(people%20here)%20studied%20English%2C%20today%20they%20earn%20fat%20salaries%20in%20IT%20companies.%20They%20say%20'Hindi%20Hindi'.%20You%20know%20well%20who%20build%20buildings.%20Those%20who%20study%20only%20Hindi%20in%20Bihar%20build%20houses%20for%20us%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20sweep%20roads%20and%20clean%20toilets%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Maran%20was%20heard%20saying%20in%20the%20video%20that%20has%20now%20gone%20viral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EI.N.D.I%20Alliance%20leader%20and%20DMK%20MP%20Dayanidhi%20Maran%20says%20Hindi%20speakers%20from%20UP%20and%20Bihar%20come%20and%20clean%20toilets%20in%20TN.%3Cbr%3E%5CnRahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar%20must%20clarify%2C%20if%20this%20is%20the%20stated%20position%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20JDU%20too.%3Cbr%3E%5CnI.N.D.I%20Alliance's%20divisive%20agenda%20is%20out%20in%20full%20force%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fi4wwLbYisW%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fi4wwLbYisW%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Amit%20Malviya%20(%40amitmalviya)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Famitmalviya%2Fstatus%2F1738828917555757521%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2024%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Mr%20Maran%20could%20not%20be%20reached%2C%20sources%20from%20the%20DMK%20have%20claimed%20it%20was%20an%20old%20video%20that%20has%20been%20recirculated%20by%20the%20BJP.%20The%20DMK%20sources%20said%20the%20BJP%20has%20recirculated%20the%20video%20to%20divert%20attention%20from%20the%20backlash%C2%A0Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20faces%20amid%20her%20face-off%20with%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%20over%20its%20demand%20for%20flood%20relief%20funds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHindi%20imposition%20is%20an%20emotive%20issue%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20the%20DMK%20has%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20agitations%20against%20alleged%20attempts%20to%20impose%20Hindi%20in%20the%20southern%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20of%20Mr%20Maran%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20sparked%20a%20political%20row%2C%20drawing%20criticism%20from%20leaders%20of%20both%20the%20BJP%20and%20INDIA%20ally%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20in%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBihar's%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20RJD%20leader%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20condemned%20the%20remarks.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20condemnable.%20Leaders%20from%20other%20states%2C%20irrespective%20of%20which%20party%20they%20belong%20to%2C%20should%20avoid%20making%20such%20remarks.%20This%20country%20is%20one.%20We%20respect%20people%20from%20other%20states%20and%20we%20expect%20the%20same.%20Such%20remarks%20should%20not%20be%20made%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DMK%20leader's%20viral%20video%20drew%20fire%20from%20Union%20Minister%20and%20Bihar%20leader%20Giriraj%20Singh.%20Mr%20Singh%20used%20the%20opportunity%20to%20launch%20a%20scathing%20attack%20on%20the%20DMK%20as%20well%20as%20its%20ally%20Congress.%20%26quot%3BThe%20language%20of%20Congress%20and%20DMK%20is%20a%20language%20to%20break%20the%20country.%20People%20from%20Bihar%2C%20wherever%20they%20go%2C%20work%20hard%2C%20and%20it%20is%20not%20a%20crime%20to%20work%20with%20self-respect.%20They%20contribute%20to%20that%20state's%20development%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20firebrand%20BJP%20leader%20accused%20DMK%20of%20insulting%20the%20country%20and%20referred%20to%20party%20leader%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin's%20comments%20on%20Sanatan%20Dharma%20that%20had%20sparked%20a%20huge%20row.%20%26quot%3BThey%20have%20done%20this%20earlier.%20They%20spoke%20about%20finishing%20Sanatan%2C%20now%20they%20are%20targeting%20labourers.%20This%20is%20unfortunate.%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20derives%20enjoyment%20from%20such%20remarks%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20leader%20Amit%20Malviya%20shared%20the%20video%2C%20saying%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20should%20clarify%20if%20the%20DMK%20leader's%20remarks%20are%20in%20line%20with%20their%20parties'%20position.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20INDIA%20parties%20influential%20in%20the%20northern%20part%20of%20the%20country%20were%20caught%20on%20a%20sticky%20wicket%20by%20Mr%20Stalin's%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20remarks.%20The%20fresh%20contro