gure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223716%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Demonstrators%20take%20part%20in%20a%20rally%20for%20equal%20rights%2C%20as%20Icelandic%20women%20strike%20for%20equality%2C%20in%20Reykjavik%2C%20Iceland%2C%20October%2024%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65730e397a3c8094d5daebd0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222050%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMost%20women%20and%20non-binary%20were%20paid%20for%20the%20day%20they%20went%20on%20strike%20%E2%80%93%20but%20some%20didn't%20have%20that%20luxury.%3Cp%3EReuters%20TV%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20some%20groups%20of%20women%20and%20non-binary%20people%20simply%20didn't%20have%20the%20option%20to%20take%20a%20paid%20day%20off%20work%20for%20the%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20very%20few%20that%20did%20not%20get%20paid%20that%20day%2C%20but%20we%20could%20see%20a%20class%20division%20in%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20%C3%9Eorbergsd%C3%B3ttir%20told%20BI.%20People%20working%20in%20cleaning%20and%20tourism%20%E2%80%93%20mainly%20of%20foreign%20origin%20%E2%80%93%20were%20less%20likely%20to%20be%20allowed%20a%20paid%20day%20off%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGriffin%2C%20from%20WomenTechIceland%2C%20said%20that%20some%20women%20had%20the%20%26quot%3Bluxury%26quot%3B%20of%20going%20on%20strike.%20Griffin%20and%20Silva%20Mu%C3%B1oz%20said%20went%20to%20a%20caf%C3%A9%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20strike%20and%20said%20they%20saw%20mainly%20foreign%20women%20workers%20who%20%26quot%3Bcouldn't%20afford%20to%20go%20on%20strike.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20can't%20have%20class%20division%20when%20you're%20having%20a%20women's%20strike%20for%20all%2C%20especially%20when%20they%20are%20subject%20to%20more%20discrimination%2C%26quot%3B%20%C3%9Eorbergsd%C3%B3ttir%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOlder%20generations%20fight%20so%20younger%20ones%20can%20flourish%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20despite%20these%20concerns%2C%20the%20women%20BI%20spoke%20to%20said%20that%20they%20largely%20felt%20safe%20living%20in%20Iceland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20Iceland%2C%20it's%20probably%20the%20safest%20place%20in%20the%20world%20to%20walk%20home%20alone%20in%20the%20dark%2C%26quot%3B%20Steinars%20said.%20Jewells%20Chambers%2C%20who%20relocated%20from%20Brooklyn%20to%20Iceland%20seven%20years%20ago%2C%20said%20that%20she%20felt%20%26quot%3Bleaps%20and%20bounds%20safer%26quot%3B%20than%20in%20New%20York%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThorhildur%20Thorarinsd%C3%B3ttir%2C%20an%20Icelander%20who%20studied%20for%20her%20masters%20in%20Denmark%2C%20said%20she%20noticed%20the%20difference%20between%20the%20two%20counties.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20shocking%20to%20see%20and%20feel%20how%20much%20Denmark%20felt%20behind%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI%20over%20email.%20%26quot%3BIt%20felt%20like%20going%20back%2010-15%20years%20in%20time%20%E2%80%A6%20I%20didn't%20feel%20as%20respected%20as%20a%20woman%20as%20I%20do%20in%20Iceland.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWomen%20BI%20spoke%20to%20largely%20said%20they%20felt%20optimistic%20about%20the%20changes%20that%20future%20generations%20would%20bring.%20Griffin%20and%20Silva%20Mu%C3%B1oz%20%E2%80%93%20both%20millennials%20%E2%80%93%20said%20that%20what%20their%20generation%20referred%20to%20as%20diversity%20and%20inclusion%20was%20just%20%26quot%3Bthe%20norm%26quot%3B%20for%20Gen%20Z.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224624%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20showing%20Valenttina%20Griffin%20and%20Alondra%20Silva%20Mu%C3%B1oz%2C%20the%20co-founder%20and%20chair%20of%20WomenTechIceland%2C%20sat%20on%20a%20sofa%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65730c2f58e7c0c29a2aed9a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223468%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EValenttina%20Griffin%20and%20Alondra%20Silva%20Mu%C3%B1oz%2C%20the%20co-founder%20and%20chair%20of%20WomenTechIceland%2C%20said%20they%20were%20excited%20for%20the%20opportunities%20that%20Gen%20Z