%20India%20(WFI)%20panel%20to%20suspend%20all%20activities%20till%20further%20orders.%20The%20centre%20also%20noted%20the%20%26quot%3Bhasty%26quot%3B%20announcement%20of%20the%20junior%20national%20contests.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sports%20ministry's%20statement%20also%20noted%20that%20the%20newly%20elected%20body%20%26quot%3Bappears%20to%20be%20(in)%20complete%20control%20of%20former%20office%20bearers%20in%20complete%20disregard%20to%20the%20Sports%20Code%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20business%20of%20WFI%2C%20the%20ministry%20said%2C%20is%20being%20run%20from%20the%20premises%20controlled%20by%20former%20office%20bearers.%20%26quot%3BWhich%20is%20also%20alleged%20premises%20wherein%20sexual%20harassment%20of%20the%20players%20have%20been%20alleged%20and%20(at)%20present%20the%20court%20in%20hearing%20the%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20the%20Sports%20Ministry's%20move%2C%20Sanjay%20Singh%20said%20he%20had%20not%20received%20any%20letter%20yet.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20in%20the%20flight.%20I've%20not%20received%20any%20letter%20yet.%20First%2C%20let%20me%20see%20the%20letter%2C%20only%20then%20I%20will%20comment.%20I%20heard%20that%20some%20activity%20has%20been%20stopped%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sports%20ministry's%20strong%20rebuke%20comes%20days%20after%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%20an%20aide%20of%20former%20WFI%20chief%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%2C%20succeeded%20him%20in%20the%20elections%20for%20the%20country's%20top%20wrestling%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%2C%20a%20six-time%20BJP%20MP%2C%20had%20to%20step%20aside%20after%20the%20country's%20top%20wrestlers%2C%20including%20Ms%20Malikkh%2C%20accused%20him%20of%20sexually%20harassing%20women%20wrestlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20wrestlers%2C%20also%20including%20Olympic%20Games%20bronze%20medallist%20Bajrang%20Punia%20and%20Commonwealth%20Games%20gold%20medallist%20V