icks%20inside%20the%20parliament.%20While%20the%20entire%20media%20ran%20with%20this%20story%2C%20a%20gut%20wrenching%20story%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fchurachandpur-manipur-kuko-zo-87-bodies%23%3A~%3Atext%3Drights-%2CIn%2520Churachandpur%252C%2520a%2520Brutal%2520and%2520Final%2520Homecoming%2520for%252087%2520People%2Cin%2520May%252C%2520eight%2520months%2520ago.%5C%22%3Ethe%20mass%20burial%20of%2087%20Kukis%20killed%20in%20Manipur%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20with%20the%20youngest%20victim%20being%20a%20month-old%20baby%20%E2%80%93%20was%20relegated%20to%20the%20inside%20pages%20or%20just%20ignored.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20new%20year%20is%20a%20coming-out%20party%20of%20sorts%20for%20Godi%20media%20that%20now%20publicly%20squabbles%20over%20a%20gas%20canister%2C%20and%20will%20black%20out%20any%20news%20that%2C%20according%20to%20their%20handlers%2C%20is%20unfit%20for%20consumption.%20Dramatic%20public%20display%20of%20outrage%20by%20the%20most%20privileged%20about%20their%20humble%20origins%20or%20their%20caste%20being%20deliberately%20maligned%20by%20harsh%20words%20is%20a%20tad%20surprising%20when%2C%20just%20yesterday%2C%20everyone%20was%20busy%20locating%20and%20consolidating%20vote%20banks%20of%20the%20poorest%20and%20most%20backward%20groups.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwho-are-our-young-andolanjeevis%5C%22%3EWho%20Are%20Our%20Young%20Andolanjeevis%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmid%20this%20cacophony%2C%20chief%20economic%20advisor%20V.%20Anantha%20Nageswaran%20in%20a%20recent%20essay%20said%20that%20India%20is%20displaying%20a%20strange%20convergence%20between%20growth%20and%20inequality.%20And%20a%20deepening%20of%20inequalities%20without%20any%20major%20push%20backs%20has%20resulted%20in%20not%20just%20malnutrition%20and%20low%20wages%20among%20the%20larger%20sections%20but%20a%20very%20alarming%20lack%20of%20access%20to%20education%20and%20health%20care%20for%20the%20poor.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20will%20directly%20impact%20and%20reduce%20growth%20potential%20of%20India%20in%20a%20rapidly%20changing%20corporate%20demand%20for%20highly%20skilled%20labour.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStrange%20to%20hear%20the%20privileged%20complain%20about%20feeling%20miserable%20and%20persecuted%20while%20the%20silence%20of%20the%20lambs%20goes%20unnoticed.%20There%20is%20little%20in%20the%20news%20about%20an%20increasingly%20vast%20number%20of%20graduates%20being%2022%25%20of%20all%20unemployed%20in%20India.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20white%20collar%20flexi%20staff%3A%20brand%20consultants%20and%20coaches%20running%20their%20own%20gigs%20or%20partnering%20with%20someone%2C%20are%20having%20a%20ball%20like%20never%20before.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20evolution%20of%20our%20corporate%20landscape%20(and%20that%20includes%20the%20media%20also)%20and%20work%20being%20redefined%20is%20a%20story%20hardly%20ever%20highlighted.%20Not%20loyalty%20but%20flexibility%20is%20the%20flavour%20of%20the%20season.%20Recruitment%20agency%20(CIEL%20HR)%20reports%2055%25%20of%20organizations%20surveyed%20across%20sectors%20are%20now%20engaging%20gig%20workers%20and%20companies%20have%20said%20that%20they%20are%20going%20to%20hire%20more%20gig%20workers%20who%20are%20flexible%2C%20scale%20their%20workforce%20as%20required%20in%20an%20atmosphere%20where%20project%20demands%20are%20changing%20swiftly%20and%20workloads%20keep%20fluctuating.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20fresh%20formal%20job%20creation%20has%20dipped%20to%20a%20seven-month%20low%20in%20October%20according%20to%20Employees%E2%80%99%20Provident%20Fund%20Organisation%20(EPFO)%20data%20while%20gig%20freelancers%E2%80%99%20earnings%20have%20grown%20by%20294%25%20according%20to%20gig%20platform%20Pick%20My%20Work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F19090359%2FIMG_1911.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22school%20education%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F19090359%2FIMG_1911.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F19090359%2FIMG_1911-300x120.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F19090359%2FIMG_1911-1024x410.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-649250%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20IT%20firms%2C%20who%20ushered%20in%20a%20media%20and%20communication%20revolution%20early%20in%20the%20century%2C%20also%20now%20prefer%20the%20gig%20industry.%20Their%20needs%20are%20changing%20ever%20since%20AI%E2%80%99s%20arrival.%20The%20last%20decade%20of%20the%2020th%20century%20saw%20designers%2C%20content%20creators%20and%20creative%20writing%20professionals%20rule%20the%20work%20space.%20But%20that%20is%20no%20longer%20the%20case.%20Staffing%20service%20CIEL%E2%80%99s%20data%20shows%20that%20top%20employers%20like%20Tata%2C%20Infosys%20and%20LTI%20Mindtree%20are%20now%20mostly%20recruiting%20freelancers%20from%20the%20gig%20industry%20that%20helps%20them%20locate%20workers%20with%20different%20skills.%20For%20enhancing%20efficiency%20and%20honing%20their%20skills%2C%20they%20need%20not%20attend%20coaching%20classes%20taught%20by%20humans.%20Superior%20guidance%20will%20be%20forthcoming%20to%20them%20from%20AI!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20is%20reminded%20of%20an%20old%20story%20about%20emperor%20Akbar%20in%20which%20the%20he%20asks%20his%20confidante%20and%20all%20weather%20man%20Birbal%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ELa%20Birbal%20koi%20aisaa%20Nar%2C%20jo%20Pir%20Bawarchi%2C%20Bhishti%2C%20Khar%3C%2Fem%3E%20(bring%20me%20a%20man%20who%20can%20be%20a%20sage%2C%20a%20chef%2C%20a%20water%20carrier%20or%20a%20donkey%20as%20per%20need)%E2%80%9D.%20The%20new%20generation%20of%20job%20seekers%20guided%20by%20AI%20will%20soon%20be%20such%20a%20multitasking%20nerd%20with%20a%20fat%20salary.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnce%20one%20falls%20into%20that%20particular%20rabbit%20hole%20guided%20by%20a%20non%20human%20entity%2C%20one%20will%20accept%20living%20without%20privacy%2C%20and%20outside%20time.%20There%20will%20be%20no%20clocking%20off%20ever%20in%20the%20redone%20work%20space%20but%20also%20no%20gossip%20sessions%20or%20friendly%20banter%20with%20colleagues%2C%20nor%20drowning%20of%20anxieties%20in%20a%20pub%20or%20hanging%20out%20at%20the%20corner%20gym%20doing%20pilates.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20writers%20will%20have%20to%20unlearn%20writing%20along%20their%20own%20whims%20and%20fancies%2C%20the%20actors%20will%20no%20longer%20act%20but%20play%20out%20the%20theme%20from%20a%20graphic%20series.%20Remember%20Batman%20and%20Archies%E2%80%99%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20painter%20need%20never%20sit%20outdoors%20to%20study%20light%20or%20form%20because%20AI%20will%20reproduce%20old%20masterpieces%20and%20more.%20It%20could%20only%20happen%20in%20this%20scenario%20that%20the%20largest%20opposition%20group%2C%20the%20Congress%20party%E2%80%99s%20online%20crowd%20funding%20effort%20%E2%80%98Donate%20for%20Desh%E2%80%99%2C%20allegedly%20met%20with%20over%2020%2C000%20bot%20attacks%20and%201%2C340%20data%20theft%20attempts%20within%2048%20hours%20of%20being%20launched.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20that%20is%20needed%20to%20divert%20public%20attention%20are%20red%20herrings%20while%20over%20a%20100%20shanties%20are%20bulldozed%20in%20one%20day%20because%20suddenly%20those%20beautification%20drives%20demand%20that%20they%20be%20removed%20as%20inessential%20and%20illegal.%20Entertainment%20and%20infotainment%20is%20the%20opium%20of%20the%20people%20today.%20Some%20of%20these%20stories%20can%20make%20one%20laugh%20till%20one%20cries.%20A%20curly%20haired%20star%20talking%20of%20struggles%20as%20a%20young%20actor%20and%20persecution%20by%20political%20and%20Bollywood%20enemies.%20A%20star%20mother%20saying%20they%20used%20to%20be%20so%20poor%20that%20only%20she%20could%20fly%20first%20class%20while%20her%20children%20flew%20in%20the%20economy%20section.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20true%20that%20many%20powerful%20mortals%20today%2C%20like%20former%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20for%20example%2C%20have%20bad%20hair%20days.%20But%20a%20profound%20misapprehension%20of%20real%20world%20among%20the%20smart%20phone%20addicted%20young%2C%20when%20whipped%20up%20cleverly%20with%20memories%20of%20a%20great%20reformer%20suffering%20unproven%20insults%20and%20abuses%2C%20can%20build%20powerful%20narratives.%20These%20help%20turn%20the%20tide%20of%20public%20sympathy%20towards%20%E2%80%98the%20wronged%20leader%E2%80%99%20like%20nothing%20else%20can.%20The%20narratives%20may%20eventually%20prove%20to%20be%20be%20toxic%20but%20in%20a%20world%20run%20by%20digits%20and%20AI%2C%20people%20will%20have%20no%20trouble%20believing%20them.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESaakhi%20is%20a%20Sunday%20column%20from%20Mrinal%20Pande%2C%20in%20which%20she%20writes%20of%20what%20she%20sees%20and%20also%20participates%20in.%20That%20has%20been%20her%20burden%20to%20bear%20ever%20since%20she%20embarked%20on%20a%20life%20as%20a%20journalist%2C%20writer%2C%20editor%2C%20author%20and%20as%20chairperson%20of%20Prasar%20Bharti.%20Her%20journey%20of%20being%20a%20witness-participant%20continues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703404300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%