india%2Fman-sets-sister-in-law-on-fire-in-madhya-pradeshs-ratlam-held%2Farticleshow%2F106247299.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2033-year-old%20woman%20was%20set%20on%20fire%20allegedly%20by%20her%20brother-in-law%20in%20broad%20daylight%20in%20Ratlam%20district%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20police%20said%20on%20Sunday.%20The%20police%20have%20arrested%20the%20accused%2C%20Suresh%20(40)%2C%20for%20the%20murder%20that%20occurred%20at%20Dhodhar%20village%20of%20Ratlam%20district%20on%20Saturday%2C%20an%20official%20said.%20Suresh%20allegedly%20attacked%20his%20sister-in-law%20Nirmala%20with%20a%20rod%20and%20poured%20petrol%20on%20her%20before%20setting%20her%20ablaze%2C%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20(SP)%20Rahul%20Kumar%20Lodha%20said.%20The%20victim%20was%20killed%20on%20the%20spot%2C%20he%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Macron's%20Republic%20Day%20Visit%20Could%20Precipitate%20the%20IAF's%20Long-Deferred%20Modernisation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F11202742%2FThe_Prime_Minister_Shri_Narendra_Modi_meeting_the_President_of_France_Mr._Emmanuel_Macron_at_Elysee_Palace_in_Paris_on_June_03_2017_2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESymbolism%20remains%20an%20important%20and%20subtle%20ingredient%20in%20bilateral%20diplomatic%20and%20national%20security%20dealings%20between%20countries.%20India%20and%20France%2C%20with%20robust%2C%20longstanding%20and%20ongoing%20materiel%20commerce%2C%20are%20certainly%20no%20exception.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHence%2C%20the%20imagery%20of%20France%E2%80%99s%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20as%20the%20chief%20guest%20at%20next%20month%E2%80%99s%20annual%20Republic%20Day%20parade%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20will%20not%20be%20entirely%20lost%20on%20many%2C%20given%20that%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20(IAF)%20has%2C%20once%20again%2C%20fast-tracked%20its%20long%20overdue%20plans%20to%20acquire%20114%20multi-role%20fighter%20aircraft%20(MRFA)%20to%20boost%20its%20flagging%20combat%20squadrons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CApart%20from%20the%20reciprocity%20in%20inviting%20President%20Macron%20for%20the%20January%2026%20spectacle%2C%20in%20return%20for%20making%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20the%20chief%20guest%20at%20France%E2%80%99s%20yearly%20Bastille%20Day%20parade%20in%20Paris%20in%20July%2C%20the%20prospect%20of%20India%20acquiring%20additional%20Dassault%20Rafales%20for%20the%20crucial%20MRFA%20tender%2C%20loomed%20in%20the%20background%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20veteran%20three-star%20IAF%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20activity%20was%20all%20a%20part%20of%20%E2%80%98discreet%20signalling%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20two%20sides%20with%20regard%20to%20these%20potential%20purchases%2C%20he%20added%2C%20declining%20to%20be%20named%20for%20fear%20of%20official%20retribution%20for%20speaking%20on%20such%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20assortment%20of%20serving%20and%20retired%20IAF%20officers%2C%20security%20officials%20and%20analysts%20broadly%20agreed.%20They%20also%20stated%20that%20the%20%E2%80%98ground%20reality%E2%80%99%20with%20regard%20to%20the%20IAF%E2%80%99s%20chances%20of%20inducting%20Rafales%20under%20its%20proposed%20MRFA%20programme%20was%20high%20on%20a%20number%20of%20counts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForemost%2C%20these%20included%20the%2036%20Rafales%20that%20the%20IAF%20had%20acquired%20in%202016%20for%20around%20%249%20billion%2C%20its%20first%20overseas%20combat%20aircraft%20procurement%20in%2023%20years%2C%20after%20the%20first%20lot%20of%20Russian%20Sukhoi%20S-30MKI%20(India)%20multi-role%20fighters%20were%20first%20imported%20in%20the%20early%201990s%20before%20their%20indigenous%20licensed%20production%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThereafter%2C%20the%20Indian%20Navy%20(IN)%20had%20earlier%20this%20year%20opted%20for%2026%20Rafale-M%20(Marine)%20fighters%2C%20including%20four%20dual-seat%20trainers%2C%20for%20embarkation%20on%20the%20%3Cem%3EINS%20Vikrant%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20its%20newly%20commissioned%20aircraft%20carrier%2C%20making%20it%20a%20total%20of%2062%20French%20combat%20aircraft%20in%20service%20with%20India%E2%80%99s%20military%2C%20all%20of%20them%20manufactured%20by%20Dassault.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20media%20reports%2C%20negotiations%20over%20cost%20and%20delivery%20schedules%20for%20the%20Rafale-Ms%20were%20underway%20in%20the%20government-to-government%20deal%20between%20Paris%20and%20New%20Delhi%2C%20and%20the%20deal%20was%20likely%20to%20be%20inked%20after%20a%20new%20Indian%20government%20came%20into%20office%20following%20parliamentary%20elections%20in%20early%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAdding%20to%20these%2062%20Rafales%20made%20eminent%20commercial%2C%20logistical%20and%20operational%20sense%20as%20the%20support%20infrastructure%20and%20servicing%20and%20maintenance%20systems%20for%20them%20had%20already%20been%20established%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20above-mentioned%20IAF%20fighter%20pilot%20veteran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20importantly%2C%20acquiring%20tried%20and%20tested%20Rafales%20would%20also%20hasten%20fighter%20inductions%20by%20dispensing%20with%20extended%20evaluation%20and%20trials%2C%20and%20in%20turn%20would%20speedily%20boost%20the%20IAFs%20fighter%20squadrons%2C%20which%20had%20depreciated%20to%2029-30%20from%20a%20sanctioned%20strength%20of%2042%2C%20he%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20industry%20officials%20said%20that%20acquiring%20supplementary%20Rafales%20would%20also%20streamline%20the%20IAF%E2%80%99s%20diverse%20fighter%20catalogue%2C%20which%20presently%20features%20seven%20different%20aircraft%20types%2C%20sustaining%20all%20of%20which%20was%20not%20only%20an%20enduring%20logistical%20nightmare%20but%20also%20a%20hugely%20expensive%20affair%20for%20the%20financially%20strapped%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20Rafales%20were%20already%20in%20%E2%80%98serious%E2%80%99%20contention%20for%20the%20MRFA%20buy%2C%20which%20envisages%20importing%20a%20squadron%20of%2018%20shortlisted%20fighters%20in%20flyaway%20condition%20from%20amongst%20seven%20models%20on%20offer%20from%20overseas%20original%20equipment%20manufacturers%20(OEMs)%20who%20had%20responded%20to%20the%20IAFs%20April%202018%20request%20for%20information%20(RfI).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remaining%2096%20platforms%20would%20be%20built%20indigenously%20via%20a%20collaborative%20venture%20between%20the%20qualified%20OEM%20and%20a%20domestic%20strategic%20partner%20from%20either%20the%20private%20or%20public%20sector%2C%20with%20progressively%20enhanced%20levels%20of%20indigenisation%2C%20in%20the%20overall%20MRFA%20deal%2C%20estimated%20at%20around%20%2425%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndustry%20and%20official%20sources%20said%20the%20MRFA%20tender%20was%20expected%20imminently%2C%20and%20senior%20IAF%20officers%20estimated%20that%20the%20initial%20number%20of%20fighters%20(114)%20could%20increase%20to%20around%20200%20units%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20possible%20export%20options%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20platforms%E2%80%99%20cost%20amortisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20six%20other%20OEMs%2C%20besides%20Dassault%2C%20who%20had%20responded%20to%20the%20IAF%E2%80%99s%20RfI%20included%20Eurofighter%20(Typhoon)%2C%20Sweden%E2%80%99s%20Saab%20(Gripen-E)%2C%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20United%20Aircraft%20Corporation%20and%20Sukhoi%20Corporation%20(MiG-35%20%E2%80%98Fulcrum-F%E2%80%99%20and%20Su-35%E2%80%99%20Flanker-E%E2%80%99)%2C%20and%20the%20US%E2%80%99s%20Boeing%20and%20Lockheed%20Martin%20(F%2FA-18%20and%20F-15EX%20and%20the%20upgraded%20F-21).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20view%20of%20the%20ongoing%20war%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20the%20IAF%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20jettisoned%20the%20evaluation%20of%20the%20two%20Russian%20fighter%20types%2C%20given%20the%20grave%20spares%20and%20components%20crisis%20it%20is%20continuing%20to%20face%20with%20regard%20to%20its%20fleet%20of%20some%2012-odd%20squadrons%20of%20around%20263%20Su-30MKIs%20and%2050-odd%20upgraded%20MiG-29M%20fighter-bombers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20at%20his%20annual%20press%20conference%20in%20October%2C%20Air%20Chief%20Marshal%20V.R.%20Chaudhuri%20had%20declared%20that%20the%20IAF%20planned%20on%20domestically%20upgrading%2084%20of%20its%20Su-30MKIs%20to%20%E2%80%98Super%20Sukhoi%E2%80%99%20status%20for%20Rs%2060%2C000%20crore%2C%20a%20venture%20that%20had%20earlier%20focused%20heavily%20on%20direct%20Russian%20involvement%2C%20which%20presently%20was%20questionable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlternately%2C%20shortlisting%20the%20Typhoon%20would%20only%20mean%20adding%20to%20the%20IAF%E2%80%99s%20massive%20continuing%20logistic%20challenges%2C%20whilst%20the%20US%E2%80%99s%20F-18%20and%20the%20F-16%20%E2%80%93%20a%20precursor%20to%20the%20F-21%20%E2%80%93%20had%20both%20been%20rejected%20by%20it%20on%20multiple%20capability%20counts%20during%20trials%20conducted%202010%20onwards%20for%20the%20binned%20Medium%20Multi-Role%20Combat%20Aircraft%20(MMRCA)%20contract%20floated%20in%202007.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaab%E2%80%99s%20Gripen-E%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20was%20a%20single-engine%20platform%2C%20and%20though%20the%20MRFA%20RfI%20had%20not%20specified%20any%20preference%20for%20single-%20or%20dual-power%20packs%2C%20the%20IAF%E2%80%99s%20intrinsic%20preference%20for%20the%20latter%20remains%20unstated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHence%2C%20by%20a%20process%20of%20elimination%2C%20the%20Rafale%20was%20more%20than%20favourably%20placed%20in%20the%20MRFA%20sweepstakes%2C%20due%20to%20its%20operational%20superiority%20over%20its%20competitors%20that%20has%20repeatedly%20been%20acknowledged%20by%20the%20IAF%20and%2C%20more%20recently%2C%20by%20the%20IN.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20there%20was%20also%20the%20abandoned%20contractual%20template%20for%20the%20terminated%20MMRCA%20tender%20in%20which%20the%20Rafale%20had%20bested%20rivals%20Typhoon%2C%20F-16C%2FD%2C%20F%2FA-18E%2FF%2C%20MiG-35%20and%20JAS%2039%20Gripen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndustry%20officials%20said%20this%20could%20%E2%80%98easily%20be%20tweaked%E2%80%99%20to%20suit%20an%20analogous%20MRFA%20purchase%20by%20resolving%20earlier%20glitches%20that%20would%20significantly%20compress%20negotiations%2C%20which%20in%20most%20instances%20stretched%20on%20interminably%2C%20way%20beyond%20the%20officially%20prescribed%20deadlines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20previous%20anomalies%20in%20the%20MMRCA%20deal%20had%20centred%20on%20insistence%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20(MoD)%20that%20Dassault%20shoulder%20eventual%20quality%20control%20responsibility%20for%20the%20108%20Rafales%20that%20were%20to%20have%20been%20licence-built%20by%20the%20state-owned%20Hindustan%20Aeronautics%20Limited%20(HAL)%20in%20Bangalore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20unwarranted%20conditionality%20had%20emerged%20as%20the%20deal-breaker%20for%20the%20MMRCA%20deal%20and%20had%20led%20to%20the%20MoD%20procuring%20just%2036%20Rafales%20in%20fly-away%20condition%20many%20years%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20geopolitically%2C%20Indian%20diplomats%2C%20security%20officials%20and%20analysts%20conceded%20it%20was%20less%20%E2%80%98arduous%E2%80%99%20conducting%20materiel%20commerce%20with%20Paris%20than%20with%20Washington%2C%20as%20the%20former%20was%20more%20flexible%20and%20pragmatic%20than%20the%20latter%2C%20especially%20with%20regard%20to%20transferring%20high-tech%20military%20knowhow%20and%20passing%20on%20source%20codes%20that%20manage%20fighter%20weapon%20and%20flight%20control%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%2C%20for%20its%20part%2C%20remained%20constrained%20by%20rigid%20export%20and%20associated%20regulations%20in%20this%20regard%2C%20and%20hidebound%20by%20personal%20political%20and%20diplomatic%20considerations%20over%20platform%20deployments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrance%2C%20on%20the%