0on%20Sunday.%20The%20star%20batter%20had%20multiple%20meetings%20with%20Cricket%20Australia%20over%20recent%20days%20to%20find%20a%20message%20that%20would%20be%20appropriate%20for%20the%20second%20Test%20this%20week%2C%20local%20media%20said.%20But%20his%20latest%20humanitarian%20gesture%20has%20been%20turned%20down%20by%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Committee%2C%20The%20Australian%20and%20Melbourne%20Age%20newspapers%20reported.%20The%20ICC%20were%20not%20immediately%20available%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhawaja%2C%20a%20Muslim%2C%20was%20stopped%20from%20wearing%20shoes%20emblazoned%20with%20the%20hand-written%20slogans%20%26quot%3BFreedom%20is%20a%20human%20right%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BAll%20lives%20are%20equal%26quot%3B%20during%20the%20first%20Test%20in%20Perth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2036-year-old%20had%20wanted%20to%20show%20his%20support%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20was%20told%20they%20flouted%20ICC%20rules%20on%20messages%20that%20relate%20to%20politics%2C%20religion%20or%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20wore%20a%20black%20armband%20during%20the%20match%20and%20was%20reprimanded%20by%20the%20ICC%2C%20but%20insisted%20afterwards%20it%20was%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bpersonal%20bereavement%26quot%3B%20and%20vowed%20to%20contest%20the%20ruling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhawaja%C2%A0spoke%20on%20Friday%20about%20how%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%20had%20affected%20him%2C%20saying%20he%20despaired%20at%20seeing%20how%20many%20children%20had%20been%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I'm%20looking%20at%20my%20Instagram%20and%20seeing%20innocent%20kids%2C%20videos%20of%20them%20dying%2C%20passing%20away%2C%20that's%20what%20hit%20me%20the%20hardest%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20have%20any%20agendas%20other%20than%20trying%20to%20shine%20a%20light%20on%20what%20I%20feel%20really%20passionately%2C%20really%20strongly%20about.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703402280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fvlorfr2_dsasd_625x300_24_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Ficc-denies-usman-khawaja-another-permission-as-gesture-row-continues-reports-4732946%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Usman%20Khawaja%20has%20been%20denied%20permission%20to%20place%20a%20peace%20symbol%20on%20his%20bat%20and%20shoes%20for%20the%20Boxing%20Day%20Test%20against%20Pakistan%2C%20reports%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Ficc-denies-usman-khawaja-another-permission-as-gesture-row-continues-reports-4732946%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Ficc-denies-usman-khawaja-another-permission-as-gesture-row-continues-reports-4732946%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Ficc-denies-usman-khawaja-another-permission-as-gesture-row-continues-reports-4732946%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Job%20Scams%20On%20The%20Rise%2C%20Entrepreneur%20Explains%20How%20To%20Identify%20And%20Avoid%20Them%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20increasing%20number%20of%20job%20scams%20has%20forced%20the%20government%20and%20many%20internet%20personalities%20to%20release%20special%20instructions%20on%20how%20to%20identify%20and%20avoid%20such%20frauds.%20On%20Saturday%2C%20entrepreneur%20and%20content%20creator%20Shruti%20Chaturvedi%20shared%20a%20video%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20the%20clip%20she%20explained%2C%20all%20the%20red%20flags%20that%20will%20help%20a%20job%20seeker%20identify%20the%20scams.%20The%20clip%20begins%20with%20Shruti%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20any%20company%20or%20a%20person%20is%20asking%20you%20to%20pay%20a%20certain%20amount%20and%20in%20return%2C%20they%20are%20offering%20you%20a%20job%20or%20an%20opportunity%20to%20earn%20money.%20Then%20a%20hundred%20out%20of%20a%20hundred%20times%20this%20will%20be%20a%20fraud.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EShe%20explained%2C%20%E2%80%9CThat%20person%20will%20lure%20you%20into%20the%20scam%20by%20flaunting%20the%20bungalows%2C%20and%20lavish%20vehicles%2C%20and%20they%20may%20also%20have%20many%20social%20media%20followers.%20There%20is%20also%20a%20possibility%20that%20big%20media%20houses%20have%20done%20good%20reports%20on%20the%20person.%20But%20still%2C%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20pay%20money%20to%20get%20employed.%20You%20only%20have%20to%20put%20in%20your%20hard%20work%20and%20efforts.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EDetailing%20about%20other%20ways%20these%20frauds%20would%20reason%20to%20seek%20the%20money%2C%20she%20continued%2C%20%E2%80%9CSometimes%20you%20will%20also%20hear%20the%20frauds%20telling%20you%20that%20they%20are%20asking%20for%20the%20money%20as%20they%20will%20provide%20you%20coaching%20and%20mentorship%20so%20that%20you%20get%20trained%20for%20the%20position.%20And%20they%20may%20also%20claim%20that%20the%20job%20seeker%20will%20be%20able%20to%20recover%20this%20amount%20in%20the%20first%20month%20or%20first%20two%20months.%20This%20is%20100%20per%20cent%20a%20fraud.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20are%20unemployed%20presently%20then%20it%20is%20not%20your%20fault%20and%20no%20one%20has%20the%20right%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20your%20situation.%20The%20frauds%20will%20try%20their%20best%20to%20lure%20you%20with%20their%20sweet%20talks.%20But%20you%20have%20to%20be%20aware%20enough%20to%20not%20get%20caught%20in%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20added%20Shruti%20Chaturvedi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ETo%20help%20job%20seekers%20identify%20between%20a%20fraud%20and%20a%20genuine%20employer%2C%20she%20also%20explained%20that%20the%20model%20of%20getting%20employed%20is%20completely%20simple.%20If%20you%20are%20selected%2C%20the%20company%20will%20give%20you%20an%20offer%20letter%20or%20a%20joining%20letter%20with%20the%20company's%20name%20on%20the%20letterhead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EJob%20seekers%20must%20also%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20company%20is%20registered%20on%20the%20official%20site%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Corporate%20Affairs%20(MCA).%20Also%20if%20the%20candidate%20isn't%20given%20any%20joining%20letter%20or%20offer%20letter%2C%20then%20at%20least%20there%20should%20be%20a%20mail%20from%20the%20company%2C%20saying%20that%20it%20is%20hiring%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20addition%2C%20it%20must%20also%20include%20generic%20information%20like%20how%20much%20the%20company%20will%20pay%20you%2C%20when%20your%20salary%20will%20be%20credited%2C%20and%20what%20will%20be%20your%20targets%20after%20which%20you%20will%20receive%20your%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EShe%20concluded%20by%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20any%20organisation%20says%20no%20to%20do%20even%20this%20much%20and%20tells%20you%20that%20you%20have%20to%20pay%20them%20for%20training%20purposes%2C%20it%20is%20a%20fraud.%20Please%20stay%20away%20from%20them.%20Even%20if%20you%20have%20to%20be%20at%20home%20for%20an%20entire%20year%2C%20still%20don't%20get%20trapped%20in%20such%20frauds.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20clip%20was%20shared%20along%20with%20the%20text%2C%20%E2%80%9CDon't%20get%20so%20motivated%20by%20motivational%20speakers%20that%20you%20get%20cheated.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22hi%5C%22%3E%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%9F%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%B5%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B2%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AA%E0%A5%80%