pped%20there%20for%20days%20before%20passersby%20noticed%20him.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20rescue%20operation%20took%2019%20hours.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20grueling%2019-hour%20operation%20on%20a%20San%20Diego%20cliffside%2C%20rescuers%20successfully%20extricated%20a%20man%20who%20was%20trapped%20from%20the%20waist%20down%20inside%20a%20crevice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20San%20Diego%20Fire%20Department%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsdfdpub.sandiego.gov%2Fincidents%2Fhome%2Findex%2F3491%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20rescuers%20were%20first%20alerted%20to%20the%20trapped%20man%20on%20Thursday%20at%203%3A40%20p.m.%2C%20after%20two%20passersby%20heard%20noises%20and%20called%20911.%20The%20man%20told%20rescuers%20he%20had%20been%20stuck%20in%20the%20hole%20for%20%26quot%3Ba%20couple%20of%20days.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fire%20department%20said%20the%20crevice's%20diameter%20was%20only%20approximately%2012%20to%2018%20inches%20in%20diameter%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhich%20caused%20extreme%20difficulty%20in%20getting%20him%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdding%20to%20the%20difficulty%20was%20the%20rising%20tide%20overnight%2C%20which%20delayed%20the%20rescuers'%20efforts%20to%20drill%20and%20dig%20around%20the%20man.%20The%20statement%20said%20a%20team%20from%20the%20San%20Bernardino%20County%20Sheriff's%20Department%20that%20specializes%20in%20cave%20rescues%20joined%20the%20efforts%20on%20Friday%20morning%2C%20and%20began%20splitting%20the%20rocks%20and%20removing%20them%20from%20around%20his%20legs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fire%20department%20said%20rescuers%20never%20left%20his%20side%20throughout%20the%20operation%2C%20and%20kept%20him%20hydrated%20with%20an%20IV%20of%20fluids%20and%20Gatorade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20was%20talking%20to%20rescuers%20most%20of%20the%20time%20but%20there%20were%20occasions%20during%20the%20night%20when%20he%20was%20briefly%20unconscious%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statem