%20now%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flarge-models-can-create-new-smaller-ai-tools-scientists-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadvances%20in%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20have%20brought%20us%20one%20step%20closer%20to%20anticipating%20the%20former.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3De548bf0bf3ad036f63b4955471fbdb01c68f028671da561711a6a0bb526cdc87%26postID%3D6586f1ca8aa214479654c1cb%26postSlug%3Dai-machine-learning-predict-death-life2vec-study-denmark-2023-12%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.nature.com%252Farticles%252Fs43588-023-00573-5%2523access-options%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20it's%20possible%20to%20make%20accurate%20predictions%20about%20a%20person's%20death%20using%20a%20subset%20of%20AI%20known%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-machine-learning%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emachine%20learning%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study's%20authors%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bsheer%20scale%26quot%3B%20of%20their%20dataset%20was%20key%20to%20their%20research.%20They%20collected%20a%20decade's%20worth%20of%20day-to-day%20records%20from%20more%20than%206%20million%20people%20living%20in%20Denmark%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dataset%20includes%20health%20records%2C%20salary%2C%20working%20hours%2C%20residences%2C%20and%20more.%20Using%20that%20data%2C%20the%20researchers%20created%20a%20deep-learning%20model%20called%20%26quot%3Blife2vec%26quot%3B%20to%20map%20out%20detailed%20sequences%20of%20an%20individual's%20life%20events%2C%20according%20to%20the%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farxiv.org%2Fpdf%2F2306.03009.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20test%20life2vec%2C%20the%20researchers%20ran%20a%20subset%20of%20the%20data%20to%20see%20if%20it%20could%20predict%20if%20someone%20had%20survived%20in%20the%20four%20years%20after%202016.%20The%20researchers%20knew%20the%20answer%2C%20but%20the%20algorithm%20did%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20test%20how%20good%20%5Blife2vec%5D%20is%2C%20we%20pick%20a%20group%20of%20100%2C000%20individuals%20where%20half%20survive%20and%20half%20die%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20study's%20lead%20author%2C%20Sune%20Lehmann%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20the%20Technical%20University%20of%20Denmark%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2023%2F12%2F22%2Fhealth%2Falgorithm-life-expectancy%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20CNN.%3C%2Fa%3E%20They%20focused%20on%20using%20individuals%20between%20the%20ages%20of%2030%20and%2055%20%E2%80%94%20when%20mortality%20is%20harder%20to%20predict.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELife2vec%20was%20right%20about%2078%25%20of%20the%20time%2C%20according%20to%20CNN.%20It%20found%20that%20individuals%20with%20high%20incomes%20or%20those%20who%20held%20managerial%20roles%20were%20more%20likely%20to%20survive.%20It%20also%20found%20that%20men%2C%20skilled%20workers%2C%20or%20individuals%20who%20had%20been%20diagnosed%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fimprove-mental-health-help-wellness-advice-practices-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emental%20health%20disorder%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20more%20likely%20to%20have%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20model%20outperformed%20existing%20%26quot%3Bstate-of-the-art%20methods%26quot%3B%20by%20about%2011%25%2C%20the%20authors%20said.%20Not%20surprisingly%2C%20life2vec%20performs%20better%20for%20groups%20with%20a%20greater%20number%20of%20health%20events%20in%20their%20records.%20The%20researchers%20found%20it%20also%20performed%20better%20with%20cohorts%20of%20younger%20people%20and%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20also%20used%20the%20model%20to%20make%20predictions%20about%20more%20subjective%20human%20details%2C%20like%20personality%20traits%2C%20which%20are%20typically%20gathered%20through%20questionnaires.%20Life2vec%20was%20able%20to%20make%20predictions%20about%20a%20host%20of%20human%20personality%20traits%20from%20a%20person's%20self-esteem%20to%20their%20sociability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20life2vec%20may%20sound%20%26quot%3Bominous%20and%20crazy%2C%26quot%3B%20it's%20likely%20to%20have%20an%20impact%20on%20work%20that's%20already%20going%20on%20in%20the%20real%20world%2C%20especially%20work%20driven%20by%20insurance%20companies%2C%20Lehmann%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2023%2F12%2F22%2Fhealth%2Falgorithm-life-expectancy%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20CNN.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20has%20also%20been%20working%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ai-predict-when-patients-die-2018-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20technology%20that%20can%20predict%20a%20person's%20death%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20analyzing%20health%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELife2vec%20is%20not%20ready%20to%20perform%20any%20%26quot%3Breal-world%20tasks%26quot%3B%20in%20its%20current%20state%20but%2C%20theoretically%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20can%20make%20any%20kind%20of%20prediction%2C%26quot%3B%20Lehmann%20told%20CNN.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-machine-learning-predict-death-life2vec-study-denmark-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703358749000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65871fcd1c5c7b8c9a0bc85e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-machine-learning-predict-death-life2vec-study-denmark-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20new%20research%20study%20using%20a%20large%20dataset%20of%206%20million%20people%20in%20Denmark%20used%20machine%20learning%20to%20predict%20when%20someone%20is%20likely%20to%20die.%22%2C%22author%22