%20not%20compensate%20for%20the%20risk%20they%20took%2C%20per%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Frat-hole-miners-uttarakhand-tunnel-rescue-9079210%2F%23%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereport%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESilkyara%20tunnel%20construction%20resumes%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPer%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Futtarkashi-tunnel-work-resumes-sans-inquiry-report-on-subsidence-at-silkyara-end%2Fcid%2F1988766%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereport%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20December%2023%2C%20a%20villager%20in%20Barkot%20told%20reporters%20that%20around%2040%20labourers%20had%20begun%20work%20on%20the%20tunnel%20and%20that%20%E2%80%9Cheavy%20equipment%20including%20auger%20machines%2C%20slurry%20machines%20and%20backhoes%E2%80%9D%20were%20pressed%20into%20action%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20December%2021.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20cordoned%20the%20area%20off%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reported%20the%20villager%20as%20saying.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20work%20on%20the%20tunnel%20%E2%80%93%20which%20collapsed%20on%20November%2012%20trapping%2041%20workers%20inside%20it%20%E2%80%93%20has%20resumed%20before%20an%20inquiry%20report%20has%20been%20prepared%2C%20reported%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20As%20per%20one%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.etvbharat.com%2Fenglish%2Fstate%2Futtarakhand%2Fworkers-returning-to-silkyara-tunnel-site-but-actual-construction-work-yet-to-pick-up-pace%2Fna20231220171627435435536%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereport%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20quoting%20anonymous%20sources%2C%20a%20government-appointed%20expert%20investigation%20team%20has%20surveyed%20the%20tunnel%20and%20was%20scheduled%20to%20submit%20a%20preliminary%20report%20to%20the%20government.%20However%2C%20no%20confirmation%20of%20this%20has%20been%20reported%20yet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20inquiry%20is%20in%20progress%20on%20the%20Silkyara%20side%20of%20the%20mountain%20tunnel%20but%20the%20construction%20company%20has%20started%20its%20work%20from%20the%20Barkot%20side%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20quoted%20Anshu%20Manish%20Khalkho%2C%20director%20of%20the%20National%20Highway%20and%20Infrastructure%20Development%20Corporation%20Limited%2C%20as%20telling%20reporters%20in%20Uttarkashi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERight%20after%20the%20trapped%20workers%20were%20rescued%20on%20November%2028%2C%20Nitin%20Gadkari%2C%20Union%20minister%20for%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Road%20Transport%20and%20Highways%20(MoRTH)%2C%20had%20also%20said%20that%20the%20government%20would%20conduct%20a%20safety%20audit%20of%20the%20tunnel.%20The%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fgeological-report-on-tunnel-shows-weak-rock-slip-circle-failure-near-silkyara-101701086300485.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20November%2027%20that%20a%20geological%20report%20submitted%20to%20the%20MoRTH%20before%20construction%20work%20on%20the%20Silkyara-Barkot%20tunnel%20project%20began%20showed%20that%20the%20proposed%20tunnel%20could%20%E2%80%9Cencounter%20weak%20rocks%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20adequate%20support%20structures%20would%20be%20required%20to%20prop%20up%20the%20weak%20rocks.%20An%20environmental%20impact%20assessment%20had%20recommended%20that%20a%203.5%20m%20escape%20tunnel%20be%20put%20in%20place%20during%20the%20construction%2C%20but%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdue-to-cost-and-time-concerns-silkyara-tunnel-project-said-no-to-separate-escape-tunnel-report%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereport%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20found%20that%20this%20was%20not%20done%20due%20to%20cost%20and%20time%20constraints.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%2041%20workers%20who%20were%20trapped%20at%20the%20Silkyara%20end%20of%20the%20tunnel%20for%2017%20days%20have%20each%20been%20awarded%20a%20compensation%20of%20Rs%201%20lakh%20%E2%80%93%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-cm-pushkar-dhami-announces-financial-aid-of-rs-1-lakh-to-each-worker-rescued-101701189334752.html%23%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eannouncement%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20Uttarakhand%20chief%20minister%20Pushkar%20Singh%20Dhami%20made%20on%20the%20same%20night%20of%20their%20rescue.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Step-motherly%20treatment%E2%80%99%3A%20Rat-hole%20miners%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20December%2021%2C%20Dhami%20handed%20over%20cheques%20of%20Rs%2050%2C000%20each%20to%20the%2012%20rat-hole%20miners%20who%20dug%20through%20the%20final%2012%20meters%20of%20debris%20when%20drilling%20machines%20and%20augers%20could%20go%20no%20further.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20money%20was%20allocated%20by%20the%20Uttarkashi%20administration%2C%20which%20also%20provided%20the%20cheques%20for%20Rs%201%20lakh%20that%20each%20of%20the%2041%20trapped%20laborers%20were%20given%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph