ref%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theaustralian.com.au%2Fsport%2Fcricket%2Fmichael-holding-backs-usmans-blackarm-band-battle-with-cricket-hypocrites%2Fnews-story%2Fd669c70df27d0b8b5db2d119582c0b39%3Famp%26nk%3D87573a089fffa43acbd4dae20f1e5119-1703339542%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Weekend%20Australian%3C%2Fem%3E%20quotes%20Holding%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20being%20%E2%80%9Cscathing%20of%20cricket%E2%80%99s%20hand-wringing%20over%20the%20issue%E2%80%9D%20Holding%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20following%20the%20Khawaja%20fiasco%20and%20I%20cannot%20say%20I%E2%80%99m%20surprised%20by%20the%20ICC%20%5BInternational%20Cricket%20Council%5D%20stance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FOnyaDon%2Fstatus%2F1738428642504622375%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3EHe%20told%20the%20newspaper%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9CIf%20it%20had%20been%20most%20other%20organisations%20that%20showed%20some%20semblance%20of%20consistency%20with%20their%20attitude%20and%20behaviour%20on%20issues%20I%20could%20claim%20surprise%2C%20but%20not%20them.%20Once%20again%20they%20show%20their%20hypocrisy%20and%20lack%20of%20moral%20standing%20as%20an%20organisation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHolding%2C%20who%20created%20an%20unusual%20moment%20in%20international%20cricket%2C%20just%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20ago%2C%20with%20his%20honest%20comments%20on%20how%20black%20cricketers%20were%20treated%20in%20a%20live%20moment%20on%20Sky%20Sports%2C%20extending%20the%20sentiment%20of%20Black%20Lives%20Matter%2C%20did%20not%20skirt%20the%20issue%20this%20time%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20ICC%20regulations%20say%20re%20messaging%20%E2%80%98approval%20shall%20not%20be%20granted%20for%20messages%20which%20relate%20to%20political%2C%20religious%20or%20racial%20activities%20or%20causes.%20So%20how%20the%20f**k%20people%20were%20allowed%20to%20take%20the%20knee%20for%20BLM%20and%20stumps%20were%20covered%20with%20LGBTQ%20colours%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20paper%20writes%20that%20this%20is%20a%20similar%20point%20made%20by%20Khawaja%20and%20his%20teammates%20who%20are%20quick%20to%20say%20they%20support%20issues%20but%20wonder%20why%20a%20phrase%20like%20%E2%80%9Cfreedom%20is%20a%20human%20right%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9Call%20lives%20are%20equal%E2%80%9D%20can%20be%20banned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAustralian%20cricket%20captain%20Pat%20Cummins%20said%20before%20the%20Test%2C%20it%20is%20hard%20to%20object%20to%20such%20sentiment.%20ICC%20allowed%20its%20participants%20to%20take%20a%20knee%20when%20the%20Black%20Lives%20Matter%20campaign%20was%20at%20its%20height.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20gesture%20was%20ring%20fenced%20and%20its%20duration%20marked%20by%20a%20series%20of%20whistles%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20toss%2C%20the%20anthem%2C%20the%20start%20of%20the%20game%20and%20the%20like%20were%20not%20disturbed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhawaja%20created%20a%20sensation%20when%20he%20wore%20shoes%20sporting%20the%20message%20%E2%80%98All%20Lives%20Matter%E2%80%99%20during%20practice%20and%20was%20asked%20by%20the%20ICC%20not%20to%20wear%20the%20shoes%20on%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FUz_Khawaja%2Fstatus%2F1734830493890404372%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3EHe%20spoke%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20defended%20his%20position.%20%E2%80%9CAll%20Lives%20are%20Equal.%20Freedom%20is%20a%20Human%20right.%20I%E2%80%99m%20raising%20my%20voice%20for%20human%20rights.%20For%20a%20humanitarian%20appeal.%20If%20you%20see%20it%20any%20other%20way.%20That%E2%80%99s%20on%20you%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhawaja%E2%80%99s%20action%20is%20said%20to%20have%20been%20driven%20by%20horrific%20events%20in%20Gaza%20which%20have%20seen%20a%20record%20number%20of%20deaths%20of%20children%20and%20civilians%20in%20such%20a%20short%20span%20of%20time%2C%20but%20he%20said%20nothing%20overtly%20about%20it%20or%20linked%20his%20gesture%20to%20that.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FUz_Khawaja%2Fstatus%2F1736680713657999851%3Fs%3