to%20tell%20the%20story%3A%20of%20the%20courage%20shown%20by%20those%20who%20chose%20to%20speak%20up%3B%20of%20the%20families%2C%20farmers%20and%20women%20activists%20who%20came%20out%20in%20support%20to%20express%20their%20anger%20in%20public%3B%20of%20the%20police%20alternatively%20choosing%20to%20look%20the%20other%20way%2C%20shunning%20its%20duty%20and%20taking%20measures%20to%20arrest%20the%20protestors%20post%20haste%2C%20at%20the%20beck%20and%20call%20of%20their%20superiors.%20This%20record%20shall%20include%20the%20inglorious%20record%20of%20the%20official%20apathy%20and%20indifference%20to%20the%20protesting%20wrestlers%20while%20showing%20overeagerness%20to%20shield%20those%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuch%20along%20the%20lines%20of%20the%20fate%20of%20the%20migrants%20during%20Corona%20captured%20in%20the%20visuals%20of%20the%20period%2C%20the%20footage%20of%20Olympians%20and%20international%20sports%20champions%20being%20dragged%20on%20the%20streets%20outside%20even%20as%20the%20new%20parliament%20building%20was%20being%20inaugurated%20on%20May%2028%20will%20go%20down%20in%20the%20annals%20of%20the%20numerous%20successes%20of%20the%20powers%20that%20be.%20These%20pictures%20%E2%80%93%20of%20the%20prime%20accused%20strutting%20about%20with%20full%20freedom%20in%20the%20newly%20inaugurated%20Parliament%20building%20even%20as%20the%20cries%20for%20justice%20of%20those%20who%20had%20brought%20fame%20and%20glory%20to%20the%20country%20could%20be%20heard%20outside%20%E2%80%93%20will%20challenge%20viewers%20to%20read%20the%20sub-text%20of%20the%20achievements%20on%20the%20governance%20front%20in%20India%2C%20led%20by%20the%20Vishwaguru%20in%20the%20times%20to%20come.%20Perhaps%20they%20will%20tell%20us%20more%20than%20the%20media%20analysts%20will%2C%20in%20times%20when%20those%20spinning%20the%20most%20successful%20yarns%20are%20bestowed%20with%20the%20responsibility%20of%20appointing%20fact-check%20bodies%20on%20whether%20online%20information%20related%20to%20the%20Union%20government%20is%20accurate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fbrij-bhushan-singhs-loyalist-elected-as-the-chief-of-wrestling-federation-of-india%5C%22%3ESakshi%20Malik%20Quits%20Wrestling%20as%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Loyalist%20Elected%20as%20WFI%20Chief%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20many%20lessons%20to%20be%20learnt%20from%20these%20unfolding%20events.%20It%20is%20clear%20that%20women%20in%20India%20have%20a%20long%20wait%20ahead%20for%20rampant%20sexual%20harassment%20to%20be%20recognised%20as%20a%20crime%20to%20be%20tackled%20head-on.%20The%20chances%20for%20women%20to%20get%20a%20level%20playing%20field%20and%20enjoy%20equality%20look%20more%20dim%20as%20this%20year%20ends%2C%20than%20they%20did%20in%20January%202023%2C%20when%20the%20star%20sportspersons%20first%20spoke%20up.%20Clearly%2C%20the%20crime%20is%20sought%20to%20be%20buried%20under%20the%20brazen%20might%20of%20power%20and%20the%20struggle%20to%20bring%20it%20out%20in%20the%20open%20shall%20perhaps%20have%20to%20wait%20for%20the%20likes%20of%20a%20Verma%20Committee%2C%20which%20had%20argued%20that%20Army%20men%20should%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20take%20cover%20under%20AFSPA.%20The%20Justice%20Verma%20Committee%20had%20opined%20that%20%E2%80%9CPersonnel%20guilty%20of%20sexual%20offences%20in%20conflict%20areas%20should%20be%20tried%20under%20ordinary%20criminal%20law.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20sharp%20contrast%20with%20the%20spirit%20displayed%20at%20that%20time%2C%20the%20impunity%20with%20which%20those%20accused%20in%20the%20WFI%20case%20may%20get%20away%20speaks%20of%20the%20turn%20of%20events%20in%20this%20country.%20The%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%20then-unknown%20young%20woman%2C%20given%20the%20name%20of%20Nirbhaya%20by%20the%20media%2C%20shocked%20the%20nation%20and%20led%20to%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20Criminal%20Law%20Amendments%20enacted%20in%202013%2C%20followed%20by%20POSH.%20In%20contrast%20with%20the%20response%20in%202013%2C%20the%20cries%20of%20internationally%20acclaimed%20sportspersons%20for%20justice%20were%20sought%20to%20be%20silenced%20with%20the%20force%20of%20might.%20Amidst%20much%20else%20that%20they%20do%2C%20those%20in%20government%2C%20entrusted%20as%20per%20law%20with%20the%20responsibility%20to%20ensure%20that%20those%20guilty%20of%20the%20crime%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20are%20punished%2C%20continue%20to%20preach%20to%20ordinary%20mortals%20about%20their%20duty%20towards%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20solidarity%20with%20the%20struggling%20wrestlers%2C%20who%20for%20now%20stand%20defeated%20and%20demoralised%2C%20women%20in%20India%20should%20set%20aside%20a%20special%20day%2F%20date%20to%20mark%20the%20need%20for%20continued%20struggle%20on%20this%20issue.%20Punishment%20of%20those%20guilty%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20is%20a%20critical%20need%20if%20women%20are%20to%20advance%20their%20struggle%20for%20equality%2C%20including%20in%20the%20sphere%20of%20work%20and%20employment.%20It%20also%20needs%20to%20be%20realised%20that%20measures%20such%20as%20reservations%20for%20women%20in%20parliament%20and%20in%20the%20legislatures%20will%20have%20meaning%20only%20if%20laws%20enacted%20to%20give%20strength%20to%20women%20are%20implemented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20the%20contours%20of%20Nari%20Shakti%20Vandan%20do%20not%20encompass%20upholding%20the%20dignity%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20sportswomen.%20That%20requires%20both%20political%20will%20on%20the%20part%20of%20governments%20in%20power%20as%20also%20power%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20people%20to%20hold%20governments%20and%20officials%20accountable.%20The%20saga%20of%20the%20wrestlers%E2%80%99%20struggle%20against%20sexual%20harassment%20%E2%80%93%20spread%20over%20the%20year%202023%20%E2%80%93%20underlines%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20struggle%20to%20ensure%20justice%20for%20women%20and%20punishment%20for%20those%20accused%20of%20crimes%20against%20women%20is%20integrally%20linked%20to%20the%20struggle%20for%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20so%20in%20times%20when%20democratically%20elected%20governments%20and%20their%20representatives%20choose%20to%20stand%20with%20those%20seen%20to%20be%20violating%20the%20law.%20The%20years%20to%20come%20may%20tell%20us%20more%20about%20how%20women%20in%20India%20look%20beyond%20the%20rhetorical%20invocation%20of%20tradition%20and%20false%20narratives%20of%20history%20to%20make%20constitutional%20guarantees%20a%20part%20of%20their%20everyday%20struggle%20for%20equality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIndu%20Agnihotri%20is%20an%20independent%20researcher%2C%20formerly%20Professor%20and%20Director%20of%20the%20Centre%20for%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Development%20Studies%2C%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703328844000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F21155114%2FEffect-38.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwfi-saga-proves-once-again-that-sexual-harassment-is-a-crime-steeped-in-power%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Any%20hope%20that%20the%20protests%20led%20by%20country's%20top%20women%20wrestlers%20would%20yield%20results%20in%20the%20form%20of%20punishment%20to%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Singh%20was%20buried%20when%20former%20WFI%20president's%20close%20aide%20was%20elected%20as%20its%20new%20chief%20on%20December%2021.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwfi-saga-proves-once-again-that-sexual-harassment-is-a-crime-steeped-in-power%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ED%20arrests%203%20more%20in%20money%20laundering%20case%20against%20Vivo-India%2C%20others%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703323853000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Fhp%2Fhome-page%2F2022-07%2F07%2Fful