0the%20eatery%20soon%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20typical%20day%20for%20Vatsala%20starts%20at%205.30%20am%20and%20before%207%20am%2C%20his%20hotel%20is%20up%20and%20running%2C%20ready%20to%20welcome%20their%20customers.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20noon%2C%20we%20soak%20the%20grains%20required%20for%20the%20next%20day%E2%80%99s%20batter.%20They%20need%20to%20soak%20for%20at%20least%20three%20to%20four%20hours.%20By%204%20pm%2C%20we%20grind%20the%20soaked%20grains%2C%20and%20by%20late%20evening%2C%20we%20add%20salt%20to%20the%20batter%2C%20mix%20well%2C%20and%20keep%20it%20for%20fermentation.%20The%20batter%20then%20rises%20enough%20to%20make%20soft%20%3Cem%3Eidlis%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20the%20morning%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22in%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EBabu%20Idli%20hotel%2C%20Halagur.%20Malavalli.%20Mandya.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FKarnataka%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Karnataka%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsribasavaraju%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40sribasavaraju%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FoBMn1U7RsV%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FoBMn1U7RsV%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20DP%20SATISH%20(%40dp_satish)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdp_satish%2Fstatus%2F1323543096458571776%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%203%2C%202020%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EBabu%20Hotel%20is%20open%20for%20business%20between%207%20am%20and%2011%20am%20every%20day.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20exhaust%20all%20our%20batter%20in%20this%20period.%20It%20takes%20us%20the%20remaining%20day%20to%20prepare%20batter%20for%20the%20next%20day.%20We%20are%20able%20to%20wind%20up%20only%20by%208%20pm%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUntil%20recently%2C%20this%20place%20was%20an%20obscure%20eatery%20located%20in%20a%20nondescript%20hamlet%20with%20a%20loyal%20customer%20base.%20But%20with%20the%20arrival%20of%20YouTubers%20and%20social%20media%20publicity%2C%20Vatsala%20says%2C%20he%20has%20gained%20popularity%20overnight%2C%20so%20much%20so%20that%20he%20might%20have%20to%20shut%20the%20business%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20earlier%2C%20our%20business%20was%20doing%20well%2C%20but%20with%20the%20internet%2C%20my%20business%20has%20flourished%20more%20than%20we%20imagined%20and%20can%20handle.%20Although%20the%20business%20is%20thriving%20now%2C%20I%20am%20exhausted%20with%20all%20the%20increased%20workload.%20I%20am%20unable%20to%20sustain%20the%20crowd%2C%20and%20I%20intend%20to%20shut%20the%20eatery%20in%20the%20near%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20hiring%20more%20people%2C%20Vatsala%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20only%20have%20two%20village%20families%20comprising%20women%20in%20their%2050s%20who%20help%20me%20to%20grind%20the%20grains.%20They%E2%80%99ve%20been%20with%20us%20for%20the%20past%2015%20to%2020%20years.%20Other%20than%20them%2C%20local%20people%20here%20are%20often%20not%20reliable.%20They%20come%20for%20a%20day%20and%20then%20disappear%20the%20next%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20why%20he%20is%20not%20considering%20expansion%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%2045%20years%20old%2C%20my%20father%20is%20in%20his%2070s%2C%20and%20my%20son%20is%20just%20five!%20Though%20popularity%20has%20come%20to%20our%20business%2C%20the%20timing%20has%20been%20unfortunate.%20It%20is%20becoming%20increasingly%20difficult%20for%20me%20to%20sustain%20this%20very%20hotel%20and%20I%20cannot%2C%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20think%20of%20opening%20any%20other%20branches.%20In%20fact%2C%20now%20I%20am%20scared%20of%20the%20social%20media%20reach%20because%20my%20only%20hope%20to%20keep%20this%20place%20up%20is%20if%20I%20get%20reliable%20employees%20or%20volunteers%20to%20share%20the%20load.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Vatsala%20feels%20