ple%20prefer%20studying%20in%20groups%2C%20some%20prefer%20to%20study%20alone%20in%20a%20room.%20That%20is%20totally%20okay%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBe%20consistent%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20Saloni%20had%20roughly%20a%20year%20for%20preparation%2C%20she%20chose%20to%20be%20consistent%20in%20her%20preparation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPreparing%20for%20UPSC%20is%20not%20a%20100-metre%20race.%20It%20is%20a%20marathon.%20Here%2C%20you%20have%20to%20study%20for%20at%20least%20a%20whole%20year.%20You%20cannot%20have%20abrupt%20moments%20of%20very%20extensive%20study%20and%20then%20go%20into%20a%20shell%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20opines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-1-1700746934.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Saloni%20is%20posted%20as%20the%20district%20collector%20of%20Mandla%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-1-1700746934.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-1-1700746934-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-1-1700746934-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-1-1700746934-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-1-1700746934-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334806%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESaloni%20is%20posted%20as%20the%20district%20collector%20of%20Mandla%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20most%20as