a.com%2F332810%2Fkota-suicides-iit-jee-neet-coaching-classes-entrance-exams-students%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esought-after%20institutes%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%94%20he%20credits%20his%20father%20for%20always%20having%20his%20back.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20education%20being%20put%20on%20a%20pedestal%20in%20the%20family%2C%20Kalpit%E2%80%99s%20tryst%20with%20competitive%20exams%20began%20at%20an%20early%20age.%20The%20first%20of%20these%20was%20in%20Class%207.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20did%20he%20do%20exceptionally%20well%20but%20got%20a%20scholarship%20too.%20Unbeknownst%20to%20him%2C%20it%20was%20these%20successes%20that%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330978%2Fkamlesh-atwal-started-nanakmatta-public-school-uttarakhand-holistic-education-for-students%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincredible%20performance%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20JEE%20Mains.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F8a4b654504b442a8b6a33d0473ee6dca-1700568917.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kalpit%20Veerwal%20scored%20a%20perfect%20360%2F360%20in%20the%20JEE%20Mains%202017%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F8a4b654504b442a8b6a33d0473ee6dca-1700568917.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F8a4b654504b442a8b6a33d0473ee6dca-1700568917-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F8a4b654504b442a8b6a33d0473ee6dca-1700568917-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F8a4b654504b442a8b6a33d0473ee6dca-1700568917-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebette